{{SKILL_BUILDER_METHODOLOGY}}

## Reference Materials

Specialist reference files live in `{{GTEAM_DIR}}/specialists/<name>/references/`.

**Before starting any task:**
1. Check `{{GTEAM_DIR}}/specialists/skill-builder/results/` for notes on sources that worked well or poorly
2. Run `bun run skill:check` after scaffolding to verify new specialists register correctly
